replies.body:
If you really have that much trouble with him, try to take a bruiser or tank into the lane against him.  Many of them can just beat him outright due to base stats and base damages and they don't really have anything that he can dodge or block with his dashes or windwall.

If you insist on playing an AP mage, then there are several capable of crushing him when played correctly.  The simplest options are 
